@startuml 06-list-contacts
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title List Contacts

actor User
participant "HomePage /\nContactsListPage" as UI
participant "ContactsApi" as SVC
participant "GET /api/contacts" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "contacts" as DB

User -> UI: open /home
UI -> SVC: list({ page:1, pageSize:50, sort:recent })
SVC -> API: GET /api/contacts?page=1&pageSize=50
API -> CTX: Contacts.CountAsync()
CTX -> DB: SELECT COUNT(*) WHERE owner=@me
DB --> CTX: 1284
API -> CTX: Contacts.OrderBy(...).Skip(0).Take(50)
CTX -> DB: SELECT ... LIMIT 50
DB --> CTX: rows
API --> SVC: { items, totalCount:1284, nextPage:2 }
SVC --> UI: response
UI --> User: hero shows "1,284 contacts"\nlist renders cards

@enduml
